Paper: hep-th/9807233

Date: 1998-07-30

Title: Fast Lane for Confinement

Authors: Jiannis Pachos (MIT)

Comments: 17 pages, no figures, REVTEX

Within the Electric Schroedinger Representation of the Yang-Mills theory theHamiltonian eigenstate and eigenvalue, as well as the Coulomb and confiningpotentials are presented for a special regularization-approximation scheme,which focuses on the ultra-local behavior of the propagator.